strings: <voice_0x01000C99><se_def>Legal!: May Chandni, with a sad soul, remember the scene that happened here a long time ago...
<voice_0x01000C9A><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ...What's that? I'm not dreaming... No... I remember you... You...
<voice_0x01000C9B><se_high>Salsa Queen<:> ...are?
<voice_0x01000CA5><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Why?
<voice_0x01000CA6><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ...sauce!
<voice_0x01000CA7><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I want to see a lot! I've been missing you for two years. When she passed away...
<voice_0x01000CA8><se_high>Sasha Quinn<:> Are you still ignoring today's messages? You have taken right decision.
<voice_0x01000CA9><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Always be kind to others. But sometimes you have to stand up. This is the King's affair.
<voice_0x01000CAA><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Everybody believes in you. You should be proud, because Askada is your land.
<voice_0x01000CAB><se_high>AshQueen<:> Yeah! They say dogs make babies in bars! He wanted us to think of a name for him!
<voice_0x01000CAC><se_def>King's Parallelogram: Psychological! Yes, I believe it was school last spring. Have you ever been there?
<voice_0x01000CAD><se_def>Phrabhavanavimok<:> Do you mean the young man? It must have a complete name.
<voice_0x01000CAE><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> The Secret
<voice_0x01000CAF><se_def>Fr Payne<:> Why? The name will be remembered That is a good name, sir!
<voice_0x01000CB0><se_high>Sasha Queen<:> Do you really have any thoughts? What is the puppy's name?
<voice_0x01000CB1><se_def>Kingphawan<:> But trust me...
<voice_0x01000CB2><se_high>Princess Sasha<:> Shut up. A few names might be helpful.
<voice_0x01000CB3><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Your Highness, you are a smart and generous person! You have to follow your instincts.
<voice_0x01000CB4><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> I am using my own name. I just decided that.
<voice_0x01000CB5><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ..In the ear
<voice_0x01000CB6><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I know why...
<voice_0x01000CB7><se_def>Rajpawan<:> ...Sasha, why are you so strong?
<voice_0x01000CB8><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Because my mother gave me strength.
<voice_0x01000CB9><se_def>Roy Parvin<:> Your mother, you left years ago...
<voice_0x01000CBA><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> I never told you this, but when I was little I was very shy, very sensitive, very fearful and my mother did everything to make me happy. .
<voice_0x01000CBB><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> I was so sad and lonely when you left...but I get it...
<voice_0x01000CBC><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> If I'm weak again, I can't be a mother
<voice_0x01000CBD><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Probably not.
<voice_0x01000CBE><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> I guess I should be strong. We need to remember his words of encouragement and all he taught us.
<voice_0x01000CBF><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> ...She will be with me forever...
<voice_0x01000CC0><se_def>King's Parallelogram: Sasha, you're right, I want to be more like you...
<voice_0x01000CC1><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Can we go to the rooftop? The weather today is beautiful. It's nice to see them enjoying the sky together.
<voice_0x01000CC2><se_high>Ash queen<:> Look! Their land extends as far as the eye can see! That is a great achievement. What an Oscar winner!
<voice_0x01000CC3><se_def>King's Parallelogram: Yeah... well done, Sasha... cute.
<voice_0x01000CC4><se_high>Queen Sasha<:> Dear king, you must be strong to live a happy life....
<voice_0x01000CC5><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ...everything you tell me is on my mind.
<voice_0x01000CC6><se_def>King's Parallelogram: I'm sorry Cha Cha... I finally opened my eyes. I'm sorry, I'm so sorry, I'm alone.
<voice_0x01000CC7><se_def>King's Parallelogram: ...I finally woke up from a long and terrible nightmare.
